3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-4-favorite-ai-tools-from-2024-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20upskill%20their%20workforces%2C%20and%20identify%20potential%20security%20weaknesses%2C%C2%A0but%20they%20are%20also%20creating%20chatbots%20and%20agents%20to%20organize%20their%20firm's%20knowledge%20and%20streamline%20routine%20tasks.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20AI%20leaders%20at%20consulting%20firms%20tend%20to%20have%20a%20handle%20on%20AI%20strategies%20that%20can%20work%20for%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20AI%20execs%20at%20five%20top%20consulting%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20Deloitte%2C%20EY%2C%20KPMG%2C%20McKinsey%2C%20and%20PwC%20%E2%80%94%20to%20share%20their%20best%20tips%20for%20using%20AI%20in%20everyday%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20leaders%20said%20they%20regularly%20used%20various%20AI%20tools%2C%20including%20models%20from%20OpenAI%2C%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20as%20well%20as%20tools%20built%20internally%2C%20like%20McKinsey's%20Lilli%2C%20EY's%20EYQ%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-prompting-parties-teach-employees-how-to-use-ai-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatPwC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20PwC's%20internal%20version%20of%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20they%20use%20AI%20and%20some%20of%20their%20advice%20for%20getting%20the%20most%20out%20of%20it.%20Responses%20are%20edited%20for%20brevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225495a8ce-fb5c-4f1b-a99e-2eded2c31539%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20you%20use%20AI%20in%20your%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%20Priest%2C%20US%20chief%20AI%20officer%20at%20PwC%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20with%20it.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20was%20doing%20some%20analysis%20on%20labor%20productivity%20and%20how%20AI%20will%20improve%20labor%20productivity.%20The%20typical%20search%20would%20produce%20labor%20statistics.%20Well%2C