b68-901c623fffd6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20go-to%20AI%20prompts%20or%20advice%20you%20have%20for%20writing%20good%20prompts%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%20Priest%2C%20PwC%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'll%20give%20some%20context%20about%20what%20I'm%20trying%20to%20do%2C%20a%20short%2C%20punchy%20question%2C%20and%20then%20ask%20follow-ups%20that%20make%20them%20increasingly%20specific%2C%20and%20then%20you%20can%20adjust%20based%20on%20what%20you're%20seeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20week%2C%20I%20travel%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20if%20I%20get%20100%20or%20200%20emails%20in%20a%20day%2C%20it's%20just%20really%20hard%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20every%20single%20one%20of%20them.%20I%20go%20into%20Microsoft%20Teams%2C%20activate%20Copilot%2C%20and%20ask%20it%20to%20review%20all%20messages%20in%20Teams%20and%20email%20and%20find%20the%20actions%20for%20me.%20I'll%20just%20spend%2015%2C%2020%20minutes%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20do%20the%20prompt%20%26quot%3BIdentify%20emails%20that%20are%20addressed%20to%20me%20directly%20or%20that%20have%20an%20action%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20produces%20the%20list.%20It's%20not%20perfect%2C%20but%20it's%20good%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20to%20cook%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20like%20to%20waste%20food%20in%20the%20refrigerator.%20So%20I%20will%20prompt%2C%20%26quot%3BCreate%20a%20recipe%20with%20these%20ingredients%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I'll%20just%20list%20the%20things%20that%20I%20want%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20in%20the%20refrigerator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERodney%20Zemmel%2C%20McKinsey%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Too%20many%20people%20are%20still%20using%20it%20to%20look%20something%20up.%20The%20trick%20is%20to%20have%20a%20dialogue%20with%20it%20and%20to%20get%20comfortable%20building%20agents%20that%20can%20execute%20simple%20tasks.%20Let%20AI%20handle%20the%2080%25%20of%20tasks%20we're%20mediocre%20at%2C%20so%20we%20can%20excel%20at%20the%20exciting%2020%25%2C%20as%20one%20of%20my%20colleagues%20likes%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMatt%20Barrington%2C%20Americas%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20EY%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EContext%20management%20is%20paramount.%20I%20keep%20separate%20AI%20%26quot%3Bworkspaces%26quot%3B%20for%20different%20focus%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20technical%20Q%26amp%3BA%20or%20drafting%20client%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20give%20the%20AI%20clear%20instructions%20about%20the%20style%20and%20depth%20of%20response%20I%20want%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BProvide%20a%20concise%2C%20bullet-point%20summary%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BAct%20as%20a%20finance%20expert%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bcite%20credible%20sources%20or%20references%20and%20provide%20links.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3f2f9f7-e0bd-4cf6-9b56-ebd0792b403f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20challenges%20are%20there%20with%20using%20AI%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%20Priest%2C%20PwC%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20is%20changing%20muscle%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20years%20developing%20a%20certain%20writing%20style%2C%20a%20certain%20research%20technique%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20change%20that.%20And%20I%20am%20better%20for%20having%20changed%20it%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20happen%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20just%20like%20anything%20that%20you%20learn%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20disciplined%20about%20learning%20it%2C%20and%20then%20it%20sticks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETodd%20Lohr%2C%20KPMG%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20connecting%20all%20my%20individual%20data%20sources%20that%20are%20disparate.%20If%20I%20want%20to%20build%20my%20own%20personal%20AI%2C%20the%20challenge%20is%20having%20access%20to%20the%20right%20information%20and%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20deliberate%20about%20addressing%20this%20challenge%20when%20I%20took%20over%20in%20my%20current%20role.%20I%20put%20everything%20in%20one%20folder%20and%20personally%20curated%20the%20content%20that%20I%20agreed%20with%20and%20liked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMatt%20Barrington%2C%20EY%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20main%20challenge%20is%20keeping%20pace%20with%20the%20innovation.%20There's%20a%20constant%20flow%20of%20new%20models%2C%20tools%2C%20and%20capabilities%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20pinpoint%20which%20option%20is%20best%20for%20a%20given%20task.%20I%20follow%20newsletters%2C%20participate%20in%20AI-focused%20events%2C%20and%20learn%20from%20AI%20practitioners%20%E2%80%94%20but%20in%20my%20view%2C%20hands-on%20experimentation%20is%20the%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20stay%20informed%20and%20find%20what%20genuinely%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20while%20these%20models%20are%20confident%20and%20impressive%2C%20they%20can%20be%20wrong.%20Always%20validate%20the%20information%20and%20output%20before%20you%20utilize%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223903ab8a-ae80-4107-97db-008b4b2c24df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20your%20clients%20want%20to%20know%20about%20incorporating%20AI%20into%20their%20business%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%20Priest%2C%20PwC%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20questions%20have%20sort%20of%20shifted.%20A%20year%20ago%2C%20they%20were%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20killer%20use%20case%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20most%20industrialized%20use%20case%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20use%20case%20that's%20going%20to%20produce%20the%20most%20savings%20or%20the%20greatest%20deficiencies%3F%26quot%3B%20Now%2C%20the%20questions%20we're%20getting%20are%20less%20about%20those%20technical%20use%20cases%20and%20they're%20much%20more%20about%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20evolve%20the%20business%20strategy%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20AI%20capabilities%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERodney%20Zemmel%2C%20McKinsey%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey%20want%20to%20understand%20how%20AI%20agents%20can%20integrate%20with%20their%20workforce%2C%20acting%20like%20talented%20interns%20who%20need%20proper%20training%20to%20be%20effective.%20We've%20also%20seen%20the%20conversation%20move%20from%20just%20productivity%20to%20growth%20and%20productivity%2C%20and%20to%20finding%20ways%20to%20do%20things%20better%20and%20faster%20than%20humans%20to%20doing%20things%20that%20no%20human%20could%20possibly%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20something%20to%20share%20about%20what%20you're%20seeing%20in%20consulting%3F%20Business%20Insider%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Email%20our%20consulting%20team%20from%20a%20nonwork%20device%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adeliverable%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Edeliverable%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20with%20your%20story%2C%20or%20ask%20for%20one%20of%20our%20reporter's%20Signal%20numbers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chiefs-top-consulting-firms-how-to-use-ai-prompts-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739097422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3de57bfebcc4d029df229%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chiefs-top-consulting-firms-how-to-use-ai-prompts-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20chiefs%20at%20top%20consultancies%2C%20including%20PwC%2C%20McKinsey%2C%20and%20Deloitte%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20how%20they%20use%20AI%20for%20their%20professional%20and%20personal%20lives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi%2CKelsey%20Vlamis%2CTim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chiefs-top-consulting-firms-how-to-use-ai-prompts-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20star