0have%20almost%20unadulterated%20freedom.%20I'm%20accountable%20to%20no%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20now%2C%20at%2029%2C%20Schrupp%20is%20committed%20to%20continuing%20to%20grow%20his%20brand.%20He%20feels%20obligated%20to%20provide%20a%20good%20product%20to%20his%20customer%20base.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20motivated%20now%20more%20than%20ever%20to%20create%20a%20robust%20and%20long-term%20business%20because%20Drink%20Wholesome%20really%20helps%20people.%20We're%20pretty%20involved%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20people's%20health%20and%20well-being%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20the%20current%20iteration%20of%20the%20business%20is%20a%20great%20fit%20for%20me%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20and%20that%20is%20something%20that%20I%20wrestle%20with%20often.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe's%20learned%20the%20importance%20of%20consistently%20evaluating%20his%20relationship%20to%20his%20business.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20ask%20yourself%2C%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20what%20you%20want%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20business.%20Because%20if%20you're%20not%20happy%20and%20you're%20not%20fulfilled%2C%20the%20business%20probably%20isn't%20going%20to%20do%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schrupp.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20that%20conversation%20often%20and%20then%20making%20changes%20as%20needed%20is%20a%20really%20important%20part%20of%20the%20process.%20There's%20no%20playbook.%20You%20can't%20watch%20a%20YouTube%20tutorial%20on%20that.%20It's%20something%20you%20have%20to%20learn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-founder-opens-up-challenges-entrepreneurship-starting-business-loneliness-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739097002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.inside