%20ports%20and%20power%20plants%20to%20defence%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIMEC%3A%20Response%20to%20China's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%20(IMEC)%20is%20a%20massive%20infrastructure%20project%20designed%20to%20connect%20India%20to%20Europe%20via%20the%20Middle%20East.%20Unlike%20China's%20BRI%2C%20which%20has%20been%20criticised%20for%20debt-trap%20diplomacy%2C%20IMEC%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20market-driven%2C%20transparent%20initiative%20that%20ensures%20participating%20nations%20retain%20control%20over%20their%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%24400%20billion%20China-Iran%20Comprehensive%20Strategic%20Partnership%20has%20raised%20concerns%20among%20global%20players.%20The%20partnership%20includes%20extensive%20cooperation%20in%20energy%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20military%20domains%2C%20potentially%20giving%20China%20a%20stronger%20foothold%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20This%20has%20further%20accelerated%20India's%20push%20to%20build%20alternative%20supply%20chains%20and%20trade%20routes%20-%20one%20of%20the%20main%20motivations%20behind%20IMEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20key%20features%20of%20IMEC%20are%20a%204%2C500-kilometre%20trade%20route%20connecting%20India%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Israel%2C%20and%20Europe.%20The%20corridor%20will%20significantly%20cut%20transit%20times%20compared%20to%20traditional%20sea%20routes.%20Partner%20nations%20will%20also%20benefit%20from%20new%20ports%2C%20rail%20networks%2C%20and%20energy%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20critical%20maritime%20chokepoints%20such%20as%20the%20Malacca%20Strait%2C%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20and%20the%20Bab%20el-Mandab%20are%20increasingly%20vulnerable%20to%20Chinese%20influence.%20According%20to%20a%20Center%20for%20International%20Maritime%20Security%20report%2C%20China%20indirectly%20supports%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20rebels%20by%20purchasing%20large%20quantities%20of%20Iranian%20oil%2C%20which%20funds%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC).%20The%20IRGC%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20supplies%20the%20Houthis%20with%20weapons%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20reportedly%20Chinese-made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20Of%20Adani%20Group%20In%20IMEC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20vast%20interests%20in%20energy%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20logistics.%20The%20conglomerate's%20strategic%20investments%20align%20closely%20with%20India's%20foreign%20policy%20objectives%20and%20directly%20challenge%20China's%20infrastructure%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group's%20acquisition%20of%20a%2070%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Israel's%20Haifa%20Port%20is%20a%20crucial%20component%20of%20IMEC.%20This%20move%20does%20not%20just%20strengthen%20India-Israel%20ties%20but%20also%20provides%20India%20a%20foothold%20in%20the%20Mediterranean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael-India%20defence%20trade%20is%20valued%20at%20over%20%2410%20billion%20annually%2C%20with%20private-sector%20engagement%20further%20strengthening%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20is%20also%20actively%20acquiring%20strategic%20ports%20across%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20Unlike%20China's%20state-controlled%20model%2C%20Adani%20operates%20as%20an%20independent%20private%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20ports%2C%20the%20company%20is%20expanding%20into%20military%20drone%20production%2C%20semiconductors%2C%20and%20clean%20energy%2C%20sectors%20that%20are%20central%20to%20India's%20economic%20future.%20The%20company%20in%20November%20last%20year%20announced%20a%20%2410%20billion%20investment%20in%20US%20energy%20infrastructure%2C%20creating%20up%20to%2015%2C000%20jobs%20in%20the%20United%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3EIndia-US%20Bilateral%20Relations%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20comes%20amid%20concerns%20over%20Trump's%20controversial%20trade%20policies.%20Last%20month%20he%20announced%20a%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20imports%20and%20an%20additional%2010%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20raising%20speculation%20about%20potential%20trade%20frictions%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20have%20steadily%20deepened%20their%20military%20and%20defence%20cooperation%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20driven%20in%20part%20by%20China's%20influence%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20and%20beyond.%20The%20upcoming%20Trump-Modi%20meeting%20is%20expected%20to%20focus%20on%20multiple%20areas%20of%20defence%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20seeks%20access%20to%20advanced%20US%20military%20technology%2C%20including%20jet%20engine%20manufacturing%2C%20drone%20technology%2C%20and%20cyber%20defence%20systems.%20Both%20countries%20have%20expanded%20military%20cooperation%20through%20exercises%20like%20Malabar%20(a%20trilateral%20naval%20exercise%20with%20Japan).%20With%20increasing%20cyber%20threats%20from%20state%20and%20non-state%20actors%2C%20cybersecurity%20cooperation%20will%20also%20be%20a%20topic%20of%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739096700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frk0ie17s_narendra-modi-donald-trump-modi-trump-afp_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-donald-trump-summit-adani-groups-imec-plan-to-counter-china-7670617%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20States%20this%20week%20for%20talks%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20global%20implications.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl