on%20legally%20obligated%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20Blanchard%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20are%20being%20are%20waiting%20for%20invoices%20to%20be%20paid.%20Several%20have%20pulled%20back%20job%20offerings%20that%20are%20needed%20to%20meet%20the%20terms%20of%20their%20grants.%20Some%20are%20having%20to%20let%20people%20go%2C%20and%20some%20can't%20make%20payroll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20EPA%20said%20it%20couldn't%20comment%20on%20the%20funding%20freeze%2C%20citing%20pending%20litigation%2C%20and%20that%20the%20agency%20is%20working%20to%20implement%20Trump's%20executive%20orders.%20The%20Agriculture%20Department%20and%20Energy%20Department%20didn't%20return%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec69652b-451c-4953-b24c-b23aa19361a9%5C%22%3EFurloughs%20and%20funding%20limbo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Funk%2C%20president%20of%20Zero%20Emissions%20Northwest%20in%20Washington%20state%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7290818592177065984%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20furloughed%20his%20staff%20due%20to%20Trump's%20executive%20orders.%20The%20company%20helps%20secure%20grants%20for%20rural%20farmers%20and%20small%20businesses%20to%20save%20on%20their%20energy%20costs%20by%20installing%20solar%20panels%20and%20energy-efficient%20appliances%2C%20among%20other%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20clients%20have%20%241.9%20million%20in%20projects%20under%20construction%20but%20over%20%24250%2C000%20in%20delayed%20reimbursements%20from%20the%20Agriculture%20Department's%20Rural%20Energy%20for%20American%20Program%2C%20which%20is%20funded%20by%20the%20IRA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20farmers%2C%20laundromat%20owners%2C%20and%20rural%20grocery%20stores%20took%20on%20debt%20and%20dipped%20into%20their%20savings%2C%20trusting%20that%20the%20grants%20they%20were%20awarded%20would%20be%20paid%2C%26quot%