%26quot%3BMet%20Some%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BDid%20Not%20Meet%26quot%3B%20ratings%2C%20the%20bottom%20two%20categories%20in%20Meta's%20assessment%20system%2C%20in%20their%20performance%20reviews.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-tells-managers-how-performance-based-job-cuts-will-work-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternal%20guidance%3C%2Fa%3E%20obtained%20by%20BI%20last%20month%2C%20managers%20must%20identify%2012%25%20to%2015%25%20of%20employees%20eligible%20for%20these%20ratings.%20Meta%20aims%20to%20reach%2010%25%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-adopts-amazon-management-strategy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3Bnon-regrettable%20attrition%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20combining%20these%20cuts%20with%20previous%20departures.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20a%20team%20had%205%25%20attrition%20in%202024%2C%20managers%20would%20need%20to%20identify%20another%207%25%20to%2010%25%20of%20their%20employees%20for%20the%20bottom%20ratings%20to%20meet%20the%20total%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Meta%20employee%20told%20BI%20that%20forcing%20managers%20to%20place%20team%20members%20into%20bottom%20categories%20for%20job%20cuts%20has%20spread%20anxiety%20through%20management%20ranks%20as%20well%20as%20rank-and-file%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20employees%20received%20a%20memo%20from%20Janelle%20Gale%2C%20Meta's%20vice%20president%20of%20HR%2C%20detailing%20how%20the%20process%20is%20supposed%20to%20work.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternal-meta-memo-shows-how-performance-based-cuts-will-work-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20affected%20employees%20will%20be%20notified%20through%20their%20work%20and%20personal%20email%20addresses%20and%20will%20lose%20access%20to%20company%20systems%20within%20an%20hour%20of%20being%20informed.%20They%20will%20receive%20severance%20package%20information%20in%20the%20same%20email.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20notifications%20will%20be%20staggered%20across%20time%20zones%2C%20with%20employees%20in%20Asia%20Pacific%20being%20notified%20first%2C%20followed%20by%20Europe%2C%20Middle%20East%20and%20Africa%2C%20and%20finally%20North%20and%20Latin%20America.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20in%20European%20countries%20including%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20Italy%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20will%20be%20exempt%20from%20this%20process%20due%20to%20local%20regulations%20and%20will%20instead%20follow%20local%20performance%20management%20processes.%20Meta%20intends%20to%20backfill%20these%20roles%20but%20the%20memo%20says%20that%20plans%20and%20timelines%20%26quot%3Bmay%20vary%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdb37689-6315-4821-bc3e-ba9ab315c272%5C%22%3EHow%20Meta%20is%20reorganizing%20itself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20cuts%20happen%2C%20the%20social-media%20giant%20is%20also%20reorganizing%20some%20of%20its%20businesses%20and%20divisions.%20Meta%20is%20bringing%20its%20Reality%20Labs%20division%20closer%20to%20its%20main%20business%2C%20reversing%20some%20of%20Zuckerberg's%202021%20reorganization%2C%20while%20simultaneously%20shaking%20up%20its%20Messenger%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20generative%20AI%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20merging%20its%20Facebook%20and%20Messenger%20teams%20under%20Facebook%20chief%20Tom%20Alison%2C%20while%20Messenger%20head%20Loredana%20Crisan%20will%20move%20to%20the%20generative%20AI%20group%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Information.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20Reality%20Labs%20division%2C%20which%20has%20lost%20nearly%20%2460%20billion%20since%202020%2C%20is%20being%20more%20tightly%20integrated%20with%20Meta's%20main%20business.%20In%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaked-memo-shows-meta-reorg-making-reality-labs-key-focus-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einternal%20memo%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20Reality%20Labs%20Chief%20Technology%20Officer%20Andrew%20Bosworth%20announced%20that%20Reality%20Labs%20has%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20a%20positive%20driver%20for%20Meta's%20overall%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-job-cuts-everything-we-know-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739095202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a6e1927bb3f854015c47e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-job-cuts-everything-we-know-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20social-media%20giant%20has%20said%20it%20is%20taking%20a%20tougher%20stance%20on%20under-performing%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pdixit%40insider.com%20(Pranav%20Dixit%2CJyoti%20Mann%2CHugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-job-cuts-everything-we-know-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Beginning%20of%20end'%3A%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20holds%20Kejriwal%20accountable%20for%20Delhi%20debacle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739095039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118087832%2Cimgsize-745565.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbeginning-of-the-end-of-aap-ex-aide-prashant-bhushan-holds-arvind-kejriwal-accountable-for-delhi-debacle%2Farticleshow%2F118087828.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prashant%20Bhushan%20has%20criticized%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20for%20AAP's%20defeat%20in%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20transforming%20the%20party%20into%20a%20corrupt%20and%20opaque%20organization.%20Bhushan%20also%20alleged%20Kejriwal's%20indulgence%20in%2