%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBeginning%20Of%20AAP's%20End%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex%20Comrade%20Blames%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20For%20Delhi%20Loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20licks%20its%20wounds%20after%20the%20Delhi%20drubbing%2C%20its%20now-expelled%20co-founder%20and%20lawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20has%20held%20his%20estranged%20brother-in-arms%20and%20AAP's%20national%20convenor%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20responsible%20for%20the%20poll%20debacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Bhushan%20accused%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20of%20changing%20the%20nature%20of%20AAP%20after%20it%20was%20founded%20as%20a%20transparent%20and%20democratic%20platform%20for%20alternative%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20party%20formed%20for%20alternative%20politics%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20transparent%2C%20accountable%20%26amp%3B%20democratic%20was%20quickly%20transformed%20by%20Arvind%20into%20a%20supremo%20dominated%2C%20non-transparent%20and%20corrupt%20party%20which%20didn't%20pursue%20a%20Lokpal%20and%20removed%20its%20own%20Lokpal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EKejriwal%20is%20largely%20responsible%20for%20AAP's%20Delhi%20debacle.%20A%20party%20formed%20for%20alternative%20politics%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20transparent%2C%20accountable%20%26amp%3B%20democratic%20was%20quickly%20transformed%20by%20Arvind%20into%20a%20supremo%20dominated%2C%20non%20transparent%20%26amp%3B%20corrupt%20party%20which%20didn't%20pursue%20a%20Lokpal%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20(%40pbhushan1)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpbhushan1%2Fstatus%2F1888234904158175665%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%208%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20built%20a%2045%20cr%20sheesh%20mahal%20for%20himself%20%26amp%3B%20began%20travelling%20in%20luxury%20cars.%20He%20binned%2033%20detailed%20Policy%20reports%20of%20expert%20committees%20set%20up%20by%20AAP%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20party%20will%20adopt%20expedient%20policies%20when%20the%20time%20comes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20is%20an%20expression%20coined%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20target%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20over%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20misuse%20of%20government%20funds%20in%20revamping%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20during%20his%20term.%20The%20BJP's%20'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20charge%20was%20central%20to%20its%20campaign%20and%20the%20AAP%20struggled%20to%20counter%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Kejriwal)%20felt%20that%20politics%20could%20be%20done%20by%20bluster%20and%20propaganda.%20This%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end%20of%20AAP%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhushan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhushan%20was%20part%20of%20the%20India%20Against%20Corruption%20movement%20led%20by%20Anna%20Hazare%20and%20worked%20alongside%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20to%20form%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%2010-Year-Old%20Warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20post%2C%20Mr%20Bhushan%20also%20shared%20a%2010-year-old%20open%20letter%20addressed%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%20He%20wrote%20the%20letter%20in%202015%20after%20AAP's%20disciplinary%20committee%20leadership%20expelled%20him%20and%20activist%20Yogendra%20Yadav%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20anti-party%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Bhushan%20compared%20their%20removal%20to%20a%20Stalinist%20purge%20of%20dissenters.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20winning%20the%20Delhi%20elections%20with%20such%20a%20thumping%20majority%2C%20when%20you%20have%20such%20good%20fortune%2C%20you%20should%20be%20showing%20your%20best%20qualities%20to%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20your%20worst%20qualities%20have%20emerged%20now.%20The%20removal%20of%20the%20Lokpal%2C%20us%20and%20others%20who%20questioned%20the%20manner%20of%20our%20removal%2C%20reminds%20one%20of%20Stalin's%20purge%20of%20dissenters%20in%20the%20Communist%20party%20of%20Russia.%20You%20should%20read%20Orwell's%20Animal%20Farm%20to%20see%20the%20parallels%20between%20Stalin's%20Russia%20and%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20our%20party%20today.%20God%20and%20history%20will%20not%20forgive%20what%20you%20are%20doing%20to%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhushan%20added%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20just%20delivering%20on%20governance%20will%20not%20help%20the%20AAP%20achieve%20its%20dream%20of%20clean%20politics.%20%26quot%3BYou%20feel%20that%20you%20can%20rectify%20everything%20by%20running%20the%20Delhi%20government%20well%20in%20the%20five%20years%20that%20you%20have.%20You%20think%20that%20if%20you%20deliver%20on%20governance%2C%20people%20will%20forget%20what%20you%20have%20done%20to%20the%20party.%20I%20wish%20you%20well%20in%20that%20endeavour.%20Even%20traditional%20political%20parties%20like%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20have%20done%20some%20governance.%20But%20the%20dream%20that%20we%20started%20with%20for%20clean%20and%20principled%20politics%20and%20corruption%20free%20governance%20was%20much%20much%20bigger.%20The%20fear%20that%20I%20have%2C%20is%20that%20after%20how%20you%20have%20behaved%20and%20the%20character%20traits%20that%20you%20have%20showed%2C%20this%20dream%20of%20clean%20and%20principled%20politics%20that%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20was%20founded%20on%20may%20well%20turn%20into%20a%20nightmare.%20But%20still%2C%20I%20wish%20you%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202015%2C%20when%20AAP%20had%20expelled%20Mr%20Bhushan%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20justified%20the%20decision%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Blimits%20were%20crossed%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bconspiracies%20hatched%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20decade-long%20rule%2C%20AAP%20was%20voted%20out%20yesterday%20as%20the%20BJP%20made%20a%20capital%20comeback%20after%2026%20years.%20The%20BJP%20won%2048%20seats%20in%20the%2070-member%20Assembly%20and%20the%20AAP%20could%20manage%20only%2022.%20The%20party's%20top%20guns%2C%20including%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20suffered%20defeat.%20Accepting%20the%20mandate%2C%20he%20congratulated%20the%20BJP%20and%20hoped%20that%20it%20would%20live%20up%20to%20the%20hopes%20and%20expectations%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Farvind-kejriwal-kumar-vishwas_650x400_41512388462.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKumar%20Vishwas%20Takes%20A%20Swipe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20AAP%20lost%20Delhi%2C%20poet%20Kumar%20Vishwas%2C%20another%20former%20party%20leader%2C%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20leadership.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20got%20the%20news%20of%20Manish%20(Sisodia)%20losing%20from%20Jangpura%2C%20my%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20apolitical%2C%20started%20crying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20had%20once%20told%20him%20'Bhaiya%2C%20you%20are%20not%20always%20going%20to%20be%20in%20power'%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20shot%20back%20saying%20'Abhi%20toh%20hai%20(I%20am%20in%20power%20today)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Vishwas%2C%20hinting%20at%20the%20AAP%20leader's%20arrogance%20when%20he%20was%20in%20power.%20Mr%20Vishwas%20expressed%20the%20pain%20he%20had%20felt%20when%20Mr%20Sisodia%2C%20his%20childhood%20friend%2C%20made%20this%20remark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20other%20parties%20must%20not%20display%20arrogance%2C%20but%20learn%20from%20the%20AAP's%20mistakes.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20others%20will%20not%20display%20this%20arrogance.%20Other%20parties%20will%20learn%20and%20profit%20from%20it.%20I%20congratulate%20the%20citizens