%20during%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharabi%20was%20filmed%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20happy%20today%20to%20return%20to%20my%20wife%20and%20daughters%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4g9vyz747eo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20completely%20unaware%C2%A0that%20his%20wife%2C%20Leanne%2C%20and%20daughters%2C%20Noya%20(16)%20and%20Yahel%20(13)%2C%20had%20been%20murdered%20in%20their%20home%20in%20Kibbutz%20Be'eri.%20As%20he%20was%20set%20to%20be%20freed%2C%20he%20was%20also%20informed%20that%20his%20brother%2C%20Yossi%20Sharabi%2C%20had%20died%20in%20captivity%20-%20his%20body%20still%20being%20held%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEli%20Sharabi%20was%20among%20three%20hostages%20freed%20by%20Hamas%20as%20part%20of%20the%20latest%20prisoner%20exchange%20deal%2C%20which%20saw%20Israel%20release%20183%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20under%20an%20internationally%20brokered%20ceasefire%20agreement.%20The%20other%20two%20hostages%2C%20Ohad%20Ben%20Ami%20and%20Or%20Levy%2C%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Red%20Cross%20before%20reuniting%20with%20their%20families%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharabi's%20UK-based%20family%20described%20their%20shock%20at%20his%20gaunt%20and%20frail%20appearance%20upon%20his%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20brother%2C%20Sharon%2C%20who%20campaigned%20tirelessly%20for%20his%20release%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Farticle-841201%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Jerusalem%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BEli%20is%20the%20last%20remnant%20of%20the%20Sharabi%20family%20still%20living%20in%20Gaza%20captivity.%20We%20have%20lost%20four%20family%20members.%20Around%20the%20Shabbat%20table%2C%20five%20chairs%20are%20missing.%20Four%20of%20them%20will%20never