%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20saw%20AAP's%20top%20guns%2C%20including%20its%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20senior%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%2C%20lose.%20Ms%20Atishi%20managed%20to%20retain%20her%20Kalkaji%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20returned%20to%20power%20in%20Delhi%20after%20more%20than%2026%20years.%20Congratulating%20party%20workers%20and%20thanking%20Delhi%20voters%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%20the%20BJP%20would%20fulfill%20its%20promises%20and%20put%20Delhi%20on%20the%20path%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20grand%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20next%20week%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20returns%20from%20his%20trip%20to%20the%20US.%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20NDA-ruled%20states%20will%20be%20invited%20for%20the%20oath%20ceremony%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20BJP%20national%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20met%20today%20to%20discuss%20government%20formation%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20too%20spoke%20to%20Mr%20Shah%20and%20Mr%20Nadda%20last%20night%20after%20the%20results%20came%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%20served%20as%20Delhi's%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20nearly%20five%20months.%20She%20had%20taken%20over%20in%20September%20last%20year%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20quit%20the%20top%20post%20after%20he%20was%20granted%20bail%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%20He%20had%20then%20said%20he%20would%20return%20to%20the%20top%20post%20after%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20AAP's%20poor%20show%20and%20his%20defeat%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20seat%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20he%20accepts%20the%20people's%20mandate.%20%26quot%3BThe%20results%20of%20the%20Delhi%20elections%20have%20been%20declared%20today%20and%20we%20accept%20the%20people's%20verdict.%20The%20people's%20decision%20is%20paramount.%20I%20congratulate%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20victory%20and%20I%20hope%20that%20it%20lives%20up%20to%20the%20hopes%20and%20expectations%20of%20the%20people%20who%20have%20given%20them%20a%20majority%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20choice%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%2C%20newly%20elected%20New%20Delhi%20MLA%20Parvesh%20Verma%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20frontrunner%20after%20he%20emerged%20as%20a%20giant%20slayer%20by%20defeating%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20two-time%20MP%20from%20West%20Delhi%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20was%20denied%20a%20parliamentary%20election%20ticket%20last%20year.%20He%20then%20jumped%20into%20the%20Assembly%20poll%20arena%2C%20took%20on%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20in%20a%20seat%20he%20had%20won%20thrice%20in%20a%20row%20and%20defeated%20him%20by%204%2C000%20votes.%20Mr%20Verma%20is%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20late%20Sahib%20Singh%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739086020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F7m1dfoc_atishi-vk-saxena-_625x300_09_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fatishi-resigns-as-delhi-cm-day-after-aaps-defeat-7669278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20handed%20over%20her%20resignation%20to%20Lt%20Governor%20V%20K%20Saxena%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20her%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20faced%20a%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fatishi-resigns-as-delhi-cm-day-after-aaps-defeat-7669278%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20hike%20in%20FDI%20limit%2C%20Bupa%20may%20raise%20stake%20in%20Niva%20Bupa%20H