2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex%20Israel%20Army%20Chief%20Admits%20Using%20Hannibal%20Directive%20Against%20Own%20Soldiers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Israeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20authorised%20the%20controversial%20Hannibal%20Directive%20during%20the%20Hamas-led%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Israel's%20Channel%2012%20Gallant%20confirmed%20giving%20the%20order%20in%20certain%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%2C%20tactically%2C%20in%20some%20places%2C%20it%20was%20given%2C%20and%20in%20other%20places%2C%20it%20was%20not%20given%2C%20and%20that%20is%20a%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20military%20protocol%20allows%20the%20use%20of%20force%20%E2%80%93%20even%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20killing%20hostages%20%E2%80%93%20to%20prevent%20captives%20from%20falling%20into%20enemy%20hands.%20The%20policy%20has%20been%20highly%20controversial%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20used%20unofficially%20in%20multiple%20conflicts.%20The%20directive%20prioritises%20preventing%20enemy%20leverage%20over%20safeguarding%20soldiers'%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EYoav%20Gallant%20admits%20the%20use%20of%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FHannibaldirective%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Hannibaldirective%3C%2Fa%3E'%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BI%20think%20tactically%20in%20some%20places%20it%20was%2C%20in%20other%20places%20it%20was%20not%2C%20and%20that%20is%20a%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Former%20Israeli%20Defense%20Minister%20told%20Channel%2012.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3F%3F%3F%3FThe%20Hannibal%20Directive%20allows%20the%20killing%20of%20Israeli%20soldiers%20and%20the%20shelling%20of%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4zaFyw6dcC%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4zaFyw6dcC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Brunella%20C.%20(%40BrunellaCapitan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBrunellaCapitan%2Fstatus%2F1887654384806379762%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20accused%20Hamas%20of%20killing%20approximately%201%2C100%20Israeli%20soldiers%20and%20civilians%20during%20the%20attack%2016%20months%20ago.%20But%20Gallant's%20admission%20points%20out%20the%20Israeli%20military's%20actions%20might%20have%20also%20killed%20some%20Israeli%20hostages%20and%20civilians.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDuring%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20deployed%20helicopters%2C%20drones%2C%20and%20tanks%20on%20its%20territory%2C%20targeting%20Hamas%20fighters%20but%20also%20striking%20Israelis%20who%20were%20being%20taken%20captive.%20Reports%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fdocument%2Fcoi-report-a-hrc-56-26-27may24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20Nations%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicate%20that%20Israeli%20attack%20helicopters%20fired%20on%20civilians%20at%20the%20Nova%20music%20festival%2C%20near%20the%20Re'im%20military%20base%2C%20leading%20to%20further%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGallant%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20pushed%20for%20a%20major%20attack%20on%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20on%20October%2011%2C%202023%2C%20just%20days%20after%20Hamas%20invaded%20from%20Gaza.%20He%20called%20the%20government's%20failure%20to%20act%20%E2%80%9CIsrael's%20greatest%20missed%20security%20opportunity.%E2%80%9D%20He%20claimed%20Israeli%20forces%20had%20intelligence%20on%20a%20Hezbollah%20meeting%2C%20where%20they%20could%20have%20targeted%20top%20leaders%2C%20including%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20and%20Iranian%20officials.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20argued%20that%20an%20early%20strike%20would%20have%20destroyed%20%E2%80%9C90%20per%20cent%20or%20more%E2%80%9D%20of%20Hezbollah's%20missile%20stockpile.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20Israel's%20%26quot%3Bbeeper%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20marked%20the%20later%20offensive%20against%20Hezbollah%2C%20was%20ready%20much%20earlier%20and%20could%20have%20been%20executed%20alongside%20the%20proposed%20strikes%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-defence%20minister%20accused%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20cabinet%20of%20delaying%20a%20potential%20ceasefire%20deal%20with%20Hamas.%20He%20claimed%20that%20a%20nearly%20identical%20agreement%20was%20on%20the%20table%20in%20April%202024%2C%20which%20could%20have%20secured%20the%20release%20of%20more%20hostages%20while%20minimising%20the%20number%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20freed.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20the%20Israeli%20government%20did%20not%20do%20everything%20it%20could%20have%20to%20return%20the%20hostages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Many%20of%20the%20251%20Israeli%20captives%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20were%20later%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20and%20friendly%20fire.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20October%207%20attack%20led%20to%20the%20resignation%20of%20Israel's%20top%20general%2C%20Herzi%20Halevi%2C%20in%20January.%20He%20cited%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterrible%20failure%E2%80%9D%20in%20security%20and%20intelligence%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20stepping%20down.%20Since%20then%2C%20Israel's%20continuous%20military%20onslaught%20in%20Gaza%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2047%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20with%20some%20estimates%20suggesting%20a%20toll%20exceeding%202%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%208%2C%20three%20Israeli%20hostages%20were%20released%3B%20in%20exchange%2C%20183%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20and%20detainees%20are%20to%20be%20released%20later%20today%2C%20according%20to%20Hamas'%20Al-Qassam%20Brigades.%20Hamas%20accused%20Israel%20of%20violating%20the%20ceasefire%20by%20delaying%20humanitarian%20aid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%2021%20Israeli%20and%20five%20Thai%20hostages%20have%20been%20freed%2C%20along%20with%20hundreds%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739082240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fdd49keno_gallant-idf-_625x300_09_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyoav-gallant-admits-to-authorising-hannibal-directive-during-october-7-attack-7663931%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Israeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20authorised%20the%20controversial%20Hannibal%20Directive%20during%20the%20Hamas-led%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyoav-gallant-admits-to-authorising-hannibal-directive-during-october-7-attack-7663931%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Releases%20Before-After%20Pics%20Of%20'Malnourished'%20Hostages%20Freed%20By%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20group%20Hamas%20on%20Saturday%20handed%20over%20three%20more%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20after%20nearly%20500%20days%20of%20captivity%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ceasefire%20deal%20with%20Israel.%20The%20gaunt%20appearances%20of%20three%20hostages%20--%20Eli%20Sharabi%2C%20Or%20Levi%20and%20Ohad%20Ben%20Ami%20--%20%C2%A0shocked%20Israelis%2C%20with%20%C2%A0Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20denouncing%20the%20Hamas%20officials%20as%20%26quot%3Bmonsters%26quot%3B%20and%20pledging%20to%20destroy%20the%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20their%20release%2C%20three%20men%20were%20made%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20Hamas-directed%20handover%20ceremony%2C%20which%20included%20hostages%20answering%20questions%20posed%20by%20a%20masked%20man%20as%20fighters%20armed%20with%20automatic%20rifles%20stood%20on%20each%20side.%20During%20the%20ceremony%20broadcast%20live%2C%20three%20men%20appeared%20thin%2C%20weak%20and%20pale%2C%20in%20worse%20condition%20than%20the%2018%20other%20hostages%20already%20freed%20under%20the%20truce%20agreed%20in%20January%20after%2015%20months%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20looked%20like%20a%20skeleton%2C%20it%20was%20awful%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20Ohad%20Ben%20Ami's%20mother-in-law%2C%20Michal%20Cohen%2C%20told%20Channel%2013%20News%20as%20she%20watched%20the%20handover%20ceremony%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20the%20sight%20of%20the%20frail%20hostages%20was%20shocking%20and%20would%20be%20addressed.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20eliminate%20Hamas%2C%20and%20we%20will%20return%20our%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%2C%20denouncing%20the%20militants%20as%20%26quot%3Bmonsters%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20handover%20during%20which%20the%20three%20emaciated%20men%20were%20compelled%20to%20speak%20on%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Israel's%20official%20social%20media%20handles%20released%20before%20and%20after%20photographs%20of%20the%20three%20men%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20words.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20no%20words.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fy8Osk7jPp5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fy8Osk7jPp5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20%D7%99%D7%A9%D7%A8%D7%90%D7%9C%20(%40Israel)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsrael%2Fstatus%2F1888275121489469484%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%208%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Poor%20Medical%20Health'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20hostages%20were%20then%20driven%20to%20Israeli%20forces%20and%20into%20Israel%2C%20where%20they%20had%20tearful%20reunions%20with%20family%20members%2C%20and%20were%20flown%20to%20hospitals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOhad%20Ben%20Ami%2C%20%C2%A0who%20was%20taken%20hostage%20from%20Kibbutz%20Be'eri%20during%20the%20Hamas-led%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20%C2%A0has%20returned%20home%20from%20Gaza%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20nutritional%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20initial%20medical%20assessment%20conducted%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20Ohad%20returned%20in%20a%20severe%20nutritional%20state%20and%20had%20lost%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20his%20body%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Gil%20Fire%2C%20deputy%20director%20at%20Ichilov%20Medical%20Center%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20said%2C%20adding%20Ben%20Ami%20had%20shown%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bresilient%20in%20spirit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20two%20men%20Or%20Levy%20and%20Eli%20Sharabi%20returned%20in%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20medical%20condition%2C%20the%20hospital%20where%20they%20are%20receiving%20care%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20consequences%20of%20491%20long%20days%20in%20captivity%20are%20evident%20on%20the%20two%20returnees%20who%20arrived%20today%20and%20their%20medical%20condition%20is%20poor.%20This%20is%20the%20fourth%20time%20in%20the%20current%20framework%20that%20we%20have%20received%20returnees%20and%20the%20situation%20is%20more%20serious%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Yael%20Frenkel%20Nir%2C%20the%20director%20of%20Sheba%20Hospital%2C%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEli%20Sharabi%20was%20also%20taken%20hostage%20from%20Kibbutz%20Be'eri%20with%20Ohad%20Ben%20Ami%2C%20while%20Or%20Levy%20was%20abducted%20that%20day%20from%20the%20Nova%20music%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20on%20Saturday%20released%20three%20more%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20after%20nearly%20500%20days%20of%20captivity%2C%20to%20the%20humanitarian%20aid%20organisation%20Red%20Cross.%20The%20three%20hostages%20--%20Eli%20Sharabi%2C%20Or%20Levi%20and%20Ohad%20Ben%20Ami%20--%20were%20released%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ceasefire%20deal%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmotional%20Reunions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20men%20had%20their%20intimate%20family%20reunions%20later%2C%20away%20from%20the%20media%20spotlight%20but%20were%20filmed%20and%20photographed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20authorities.%20%26quot%3BI%20left%20XXL%20and%20came%20back%20medium%2C%26quot%3B%20joked%20the%2056-year-old%2C%20who%2C%20according%20to%20doctors%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20had%20lost%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20weight%20in%20captivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExtremely%20thin%20Ohad%20Ben%20Ami%20found%20the%20strength%20to%20run%20toward%20his%20daughters%2C%20even%20cracking%20a%20joke%20during%20their%20emotional%20reunion%2C%20filled%20with%20both%20joy%20and%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20missed%20you%20so%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20of%20Or%20Levy%2C%20Geula%2C%20said%20as%20she%20hugged%20her%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20hostages%20face%20a%20painful%20return.%20Sharabi's%20two%20teenage%20daughters%20and%20his%20British-born%20wife%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Kibbutz%20Be'eri%2C%20where%20one%20in%2010%20residents%20was%20killed.%20Israel's%20Channel%2012%20said%20Sharabi%20had%20not%20been%20told%20about%20their%20deaths%20and%20asked%20where%20they%20were%20when%20he%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDraped%20in%20an%20Israeli%20flag%2C%20Sharabi%20was%20welcomed%20with%20tears%20at%20Sheba%20Hospital%20in%20Ramat%20Gan%20by%20his%20two%20sisters%20and%20brother%2C%20his%20head%20covered%20with%20a%20talith%2C%20the%20Jewish%20prayer%20shawl.%20The%20reunion%20of%20Levy%20with%20his%20family%20was%20a%20sober%20one%2C%20marked%20by%20long%20embraces%20and%20crying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Two-Faced%20Story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20exchange%20for%20the%20hostages'%20release%2C%20Israel%20freed%20183%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20some%20convicted%20of%20involvement%20in%20attacks%20that%20killed%20dozens%20of%20people%2C%20as%20well%20as%20111%20detained%20in%20Gaza%20during%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20those%20released%2C%2041%20returned%20to%20the%20West%20Bank%20city%20of%20Ramallah%2C%20four%20were%20released%20in%20Israeli-annexed%20East%20Jerusalem%2C%20131%20were%20sent%20to%20Gaza%20and%20seven%20were%20deported%20to%20Egypt.%20However%2C%20their%20families%20were%20forbidden%20from%20celebrating%20their%20return%20by%20Israeli%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bconveyed%20messages%20that%20celebrations%20and%20processions%20in%20support%20of%20terrorism%20are%20prohibited%20during%20the%20release%20of%20the%20terrorists%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ramallah%2C%20one%20prisoner%20was%20helped%20off%20the%20bus%20in%20the%20arms%20of%20a%20medic%20while%20another%20held%20his%20oxygen%20bottle.%20Abdullah%20al-Zaghari%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Prisoners'%20Club%2C%20said%20that%20seven%20of%20the%20freed%20prisoners%20were%20transferred%20to%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20prisoners%20who%20were%20released%20today%20are%20in%20need%20of%20medical%20care%2C%20treatment%20and%20examinations%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20brutality%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20during%20the%20past%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%9A%A1%EF%B8%8FBREAKING%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEnglish%20testimony%20of%20Palestinian%20hostage%20Ibrahim%20Mohammad%20Al-Shawish%20who%20was%20released%20today%20by%20Israel.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%2045%20days%2C%20he%20was%20blindfolded%2C%20shackled%2C%20and%20forced%20to%20kneel%2C%20before%20being%20transferred%20to%20Naqab%20(Negev)%20prison%2C%20where%20he%20suf