%20with%20the%20aircraft's%20fuselage%20and%20a%20nearby%20bus%20engulfed%20in%20flames.%20Firefighters%20responded%20to%20the%20scene%2C%20working%20to%20extinguish%20the%20blaze%20and%20prevent%20further%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENew%20footage%20of%20the%20Plane%20Crash%20in%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%20Brazil%2C%20as%20the%20Aircraft%20went%20down%20crashing%20into%20a%20bus%20just%20after%20takeoff%2C%20killing%20the%20pilot%20and%20co-pilot%20and%20injuring%206%20others%20including%201%20woman%20on%20the%20bus%20and%20a%20person%20on%20a%20motorcycle.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9QoKjSTHXs%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9QoKjSTHXs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Moshe%20(%40MosheDe_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMosheDe_%2Fstatus%2F1887919195238563871%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20crash%20occurred%20on%20a%20bustling%20avenue%20lined%20with%20office%20buildings%2C%20and%20near%20a%20major%20transportation%20hub%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20key%20bus%2C%20train%2C%20and%20subway%20station.%20The%20area%20was%20likely%20filled%20with%20commuters%20and%20pedestrians%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20yet%20to%20determine%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20crash%2C%20which%20occurred%20less%20than%203%20miles%20(5%20kilometres)%20from%20the%20private%20airport%20where%20the%20plane%20had%20taken%20off%20just%20minutes%20earlier.%20The%20Brazilian%20Air%20Force%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20conduct%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr%20Carpena%20was%20a%20Brazilian%20lawyer%2C%20motivational%20speaker%2C%20and%20law%20professor.%20He