.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPink-2-1_11zon-1738859803-1738988938-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPink-2-1_11zon-1738859803-1738988938-1200x675.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPink-2-1_11zon-1738859803-1738988938-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-404562%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221898%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECigarette%20butt%20fibres%20are%20collected%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20transformed%20into%20plush%20toys.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20traditional%20waste%20bins%2C%20our%20V%20bins%20are%20specifically%20designed%20to%20collect%20only%20cigarette%20butts.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20waste%20remains%20separate%20from%20other%20trash%2C%20preventing%20it%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325564%2Fthe-disposal-company-bhagyashree-bhansali-waste-plastic-credit-recycle-mumbai-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eending%20up%20in%20landfills%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20contributing%20to%20environmental%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20they%20are%20both%20waterproof%20and%20fireproof%2C%20making%20them%20safe%20for%20public%20spaces.%E2%80%9D%20In%20six%20years%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20successfully%20installed%20over%202%2C00%2C000%20V%20bins%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20V%20bins%20in%20place%2C%20Code%20Effort%20began%20its%20recycling%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20collected%20cigarette%20butts%20are%20transported%20to%20our%20facility%20in%20Noida%2C%20Sector%20134%2C%20where%20they%20undergo%20a%20meticulous%20process%20to%20separate%20their%20components.%20The%20waste%20is%20broken%20down%20into%20three%20key%20parts%2C%20the%20fibre%20(cotton-like%20material)%2C%20the%20paper%20