e%20sure%20tigers%20had%20enough%20food%20to%20eat%20by%20protecting%20deer%20and%20other%20animals%20that%20tigers%20hunt%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20helped%20the%20people%20who%20live%20near%20tigers%20by%20giving%20them%20support%20and%20money%20if%20and%20when%20they%20faced%20problems%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadvendradev%20Vikramsinh%20Jhala%2C%20the%20study%E2%80%99s%20lead%20author%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20think%20human%20densities%20are%20detrimental%20to%20conservation%20of%20large%20carnivores.%20But%20more%20than%20density%2C%20it%20is%20the%20attitude%20of%20people%20that%20matters.%E2%80%9D%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20despite%20having%20a%20lower%20population%20density%2C%20Malaysia%20has%20not%20successfully%20revived%20its%20tiger%20population%20due%20to%20different%20socio-economic%20and%20conservation%20approaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F23140155%2Ftiger-watch-4.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiger%20Family%20Having%20Fun%20in%20the%20Wild%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-233474%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETigers%20have%20adapted%20to%20landscapes%20shared%20by%20nearly%2060%20million%20people%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20like%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F393021%2Fbilly-arjan-singh-wildlife-conservationist-dudhwa-forest-tiger-haven-society%2F%5C%22%20t